	<text>
		<body>
			<pb n="1"/>
				<p rend="align(right)"><addressee>Rev Dr I. Leeser</addressee> <placeName>Phila</placeName></p>
				<p><date>20 Feb</date></p>
			<p rend="indent(1)"><placeName>Washington&#44; D. C</placeName>.</p>
				<p rend="align(right)"><add>Hebrew</add></p>
				<p rend="align(right)"><add>Hebrew</add></p>
				<p>Dear Doctor&#33;</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">I learned there are 2 Candidates<lb/> already for the Surgeonship of the Jewish Hospital<lb/> before its being published yet.  I do not desire to<lb/> compete if there is but little chance&#44; and would beg<lb/> you to inform me whether you deem it worthwhile<lb/> that I should run the risk of not being elected&#44; as I have<lb/> no estimate of the Salary and would execute efforts to<lb/> get it&#44; only if it yields a good chance.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">The points I could honestly lay stress upon for<lb/> competition are chiefly my thorough knowledge of Hos&#45;<lb/>pital routine&#44; language &#38; acquaintance with the leading<lb/> Physicians of <placeName>Phila</placeName> in critical cases for consultation<lb/> the particular empirical attention I devoted to the peculiar<lb/> <hi rend="underline">types of disease</hi> as they appear <hi rend="underline">in this country</hi><lb/> different from those abroad&#44; how they manifest themselves<lb/> in foreigners etc and if also of some avail&#8212;<lb/> my acquaintance with the <hi rend="underline">virtues</hi><add>&#63;</add> desirable to</p>
			<pb n="2"/>
				<p>be familiar with for a Jewish Hospital<lb/> Surgeon.</p>
			<p rend="indent(2)">With regards from my family</p>
			<p rend="indent(3)">Your</p>
			<p rend="indent(4)">Obdt servt</p>
			<p rend="indent(3)"><persName role="author">Dr L Schoney</persName></p>
			<p rend="indent(3)"><placeName>office 262 Pa Av</placeName></p>
				<p>PS.</p>
				<p>Please to send me one of your last<lb/> &#8220;Occident&#44;&#8221; that I can cut conveniently<lb/> for the same my treatise on the &#8220;Hag<lb/>drean&#8221;<add>&#63;</add> entitled &#8220;<sic>Sanatary</sic> institutions<lb/> of the Hebrews&#8221; which is as yet in loose<lb/> sheets and not arranged properly</p>
			<p rend="indent(3)"><persName role="author">LS</persName></p>
			<pb n="3"/>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>&#44; <date>August 15th&#44; 1865</date>.</p>
				<p><persName>Mr Max Friedman</persName></p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">To The Jewish Hospital Association&#44; Dr.</p>
				<p>For your donation to the Purchase Fund&#44; &#36;100.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Received Payment.</p>
			<p rend="indent(2)"><persName>Mayer Sulzberger</persName></p>
			<p rend="indent(4)">Secretary.</p>
		</body>
